From: XR1710G-YYH-OC Builder <builder@xr1710g.local>
Date: 2026-07-13
Subject: [PATCH] xr1710g: add UPnP, v2ray-geoip/geosite and i18n packs

Add the user-requested extra packages to the XR1710G device package
list so they are pulled into the image by default:

  * luci-app-upnp + luci-i18n-upnp-zh-cn
    LuCI front-end for miniupnpd. The matching miniupnpd-nftables
    backend is selected through .config.

  * v2ray-geoip + v2ray-geosite
    GeoIP database and geosite list used by v2ray-core / xray-core
    based proxies. These are data-only packages (no LuCI page).
---
--- a/target/linux/airoha/image/an7581.mk
+++ b/target/linux/airoha/image/an7581.mk
@@ -140,12 +140,15 @@
 		    kmod-i2c-an7581 kmod-hwmon-nct7802 \
 		    kmod-mt7996-firmware kmod-phy-realtek rtl826x-firmware \
 		    luci \
-		    luci-app-firewall luci-app-mlo \
+		    luci-app-firewall luci-app-mlo  luci-app-upnp \
 		    luci-app-package-manager \
 		    luci-i18n-mlo-zh-cn \
+		    luci-i18n-upnp-zh-cn \
 		    luci-mod-admin-full \
 		    luci-proto-ppp luci-theme-bootstrap \
 		    luci-theme-argon luci-i18n-argon-zh-cn \
+		    v2ray-geoip \
+		    v2ray-geosite \
 		    rpcd-mod-rrdns uhttpd uhttpd-mod-ubus \
 		    wpad-basic-mbedtls
   UBINIZE_OPTS := -E 5
-- 
